# Requirement: Docker Build Optimization
# Location: Technical Specifications/4.5 Development & Deployment
# Description: Excludes unnecessary files and directories from Docker builds to optimize image size and build performance.

# Dependencies and package management
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-debug.log
yarn-error.log
.npm/
.yarn/
package-lock.json
yarn.lock

